"""
        Test that the equality operator returns True when comparing two
        PrivateKey objects with different data.
        """
a = PrivateKey(enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.RSA, 2048, self.bytes_2048,
    enums.KeyFormatType.PKCS_8)
b = PrivateKey(enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.RSA, 2048, self.bytes_2048,
    enums.KeyFormatType.PKCS_1)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
